high_descs: Turn left and face the oven on your left.
Take the pan from the stove on the left of the stove.
Turn left and face the fridge on your right.
Place the pan inside of the fridge for a little then take it out.
Turn right then face the counter on the left of the stove.
Place the pan on the counter in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold pan on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around, go to the stove.
Pick up the left pan on the stove.
Turn left, bring the pan to the fridge.
Chill the pan in the fridge.
Take the chilled pan right, to the counter right of the fridge.
Put the pan on the back of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan on the counter.

high_descs: turn around, take the pan off the stove
head to the left, open the fridge
put the pan in the fridge
close the door to the fridge for 8 seconds
open the door to the fridge, take the pan out, close the door
head to the left, put the pan on the counter
anns.task_desc: put the pan in the fridge for 8 seconds, put the pan on the counter
